1. *Signal* je bio da se vratiš kući. (The signal was to come back home.)

2. On je uputio *signal* da je sve u redu. (He gave a signal that everything was okay.)

3. Njegov *signal* je bio da odemo. (His signal was to go away.)

4. Primio je *signal* da se pomeri. (He received a signal to move.)

5. Ona je dobila *signal* da se pomeri. (She got the signal to move.)

6. Kompjuter je emitovao *signal* za obaveštenje. (The computer emitted a signal for notification.)